# Icon Button Tooltips

Icon-only buttons must expose their action via hover tooltip. Do not rely on `title` alone.

## Rules

- Use `IconTipButton` from `@/components/ui/icon-tip-button` for icon-only actions
- `label` must be a short Chinese verb phrase matching the action (e.g. `删除`, `回滚`, `对比`)
- Always set `aria-label={label}` (handled by `IconTipButton`)
- Prefer tooltip over visible text when space is tight; keep toolbar/list rows compact

## Example

```tsx
import { IconTipButton } from "@/components/ui/icon-tip-button";
import { Trash2 } from "lucide-react";

<IconTipButton
  size="icon"
  variant="ghost"
  className="h-7 w-7"
  label="删除"
  onClick={handleDelete}
>
  <Trash2 className="h-3.5 w-3.5" />
</IconTipButton>
```

## Avoid

```tsx
// ❌ title only — inconsistent, poor a11y
<Button size="icon" title="删除">...</Button>
```
